body:
Replace `<connection-string>` with the connection string for your
Atlas cluster or local Atlas deployment.

Update `Program.cs` to initialize the `DataService` and call the
method to perform the query.

```csharp
using query_quick_start;

var dataService = new DataService();
var results = dataService.PerformVectorQuery();
if (results != null)
{
	foreach (var document in results)
	{
		Console.WriteLine(document);
	}
}
else
{
	Console.WriteLine("The query returned no results.");
}
```

Save the file, and then compile and run your project to perform the query.

